        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Covenant School Heroes Congressional Gold Medal Act</b></p> <p>This bill provides for the award of Congressional Gold Medals to Officer Michael Collazo and Officer Rex Englebert of the Metropolitan Nashville Police Department in recognition of their exceptional bravery and valor in confronting an active shooter at The Covenant School in Nashville, Tennessee.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
